1
00:00:00,643 --> 00:00:04,652
[Never Too Late]

2
00:00:04,652 --> 00:00:08,396
[Xiangyang Middle School]
[Episode 8]

3
00:00:08,396 --> 00:00:11,860
- So, you wanted to come here with me.
- Yes.

4
00:00:12,999 --> 00:00:16,420
It's been ten years. The school doesn't seem to have changed much.

5
00:00:16,420 --> 00:00:18,739
You don’t think?

6
00:00:18,739 --> 00:00:21,879
Now, the children in the village don't go to this school anymore.

7
00:00:21,879 --> 00:00:25,119
Look, people have started farming here.

8
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:28,100
So many memories.

9
00:00:28,100 --> 00:00:30,160
Do you still remember the second half of our senior year?

10
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:32,460
We used to meet at the village entrance.

11
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:34,680
At that time, my bicycle often broke down,

12
00:00:34,680 --> 00:00:37,679
and I had to walk to school.

13
00:00:37,679 --> 00:00:38,760
I remember.

14
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:42,720
Your bicycle that often broke down had been kept for a year.

15
00:00:42,720 --> 00:00:45,259
- Actually, that was because I—
- Okay, okay.

16
00:00:45,259 --> 00:00:47,320
It's in the past. Why bring it up?

17
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,360
You must have been annoyed by me at that time.

18
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:51,380
- I wasn't.
- Think of me as naive.

19
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:53,359
Jiang Xile, that's not what I mean.

20
00:00:53,359 --> 00:00:55,420
- Actually, every time it was because—
- Okay, okay.

21
00:00:55,420 --> 00:00:58,279
I told you not to bring it up anymore.

22
00:00:58,959 --> 00:01:01,808
- No, I… I haven't…
- Oh no.

23
00:01:01,808 --> 00:01:05,800
- I haven't finished my words yet.
- Why would my fourth aunt-in-law be farming in the school?

24
00:01:06,359 --> 00:01:08,200
Let's go, let's go.

25
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,960
Jiang Xile.

26
00:01:12,319 --> 00:01:16,060
- Why are you hiding from your fourth aunt-in-law?
- Because of Zhang Ping'an.

27
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:20,060
- Come closer, quick, quick.
- What does Zhang Ping'an have to do with it?

28
00:01:20,060 --> 00:01:24,939
Zhang Ping'an is my fourth aunt-in-law's niece's sister's husband's cousin's son.

29
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,840
What kind of relationship is that?

30
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:31,700
She's coming. Let's go. Quick, quick.

31
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:37,024
Quick.

32
00:01:37,958 --> 00:01:44,608
♫ You are the love that's out of reach ♫

33
00:01:44,608 --> 00:01:50,177
♫ But I'm waiting like a child ♫

34
00:01:50,177 --> 00:01:57,040
♫ Endless like sailing, not afraid of being blown away by the wind ♫

35
00:01:57,040 --> 00:02:02,420
♫ The moonlight confesses in my place as I wake up ♫

36
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:05,532
♫ How did I meet you? ♫

37
00:02:05,532 --> 00:02:10,400
♫ I wait for you to give me your embrace in the mundane world ♫

38
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:17,048
♫ The past, present, and future have all stopped for you ♫

39
00:02:17,048 --> 00:02:24,879
♫ As you walk towards me, dreams are pushed aside ♫

40
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:26,719
Xile.

41
00:02:30,619 --> 00:02:34,399
You young people, why are you playing in the water and kissing here?

42
00:02:34,399 --> 00:02:36,660
- Auntie, it's not what you think.
- Xile.

43
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:39,920
Why do you lie to me? I'm not an outsider.

44
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:42,520
Do you think I’m on Xiao Zhang’s side and not yours?

45
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:45,000
Just tell me directly you have a boyfriend.

46
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:49,139
No, no, you really misunderstood. Aunt,ie the thing is…

47
00:02:49,799 --> 00:02:53,479
Le Le, your aunt-in-law is not an outsider.

48
00:02:53,479 --> 00:02:56,740
Since we just began our relationship, why hide it from her?

49
00:02:56,740 --> 00:02:58,120
Exactly, exactly.

50
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,559
He indeed looks better than Ping'an.

51
00:03:00,559 --> 00:03:04,440
Auntie, we just started our relationship. We want to spend some more time by ourselves.

52
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:07,519
Can we visit you in a few days?

53
00:03:07,519 --> 00:03:10,020
Okay, okay. I'm leaving.

54
00:03:10,020 --> 00:03:12,599
- Okay. No problem.
- Have fun.

55
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:14,900
- Be careful.
- Auntie…

56
00:03:14,900 --> 00:03:17,720
What if she tells my Mom? The misunderstanding would be huge.

57
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,160
Then explain it clearly.

58
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,300
How to explain it clearly?

59
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:22,860
I…

60
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:27,500
Don't explain. You can't explain clearly.

61
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:32,980
Why are you laughing? You were laughing all the way.

62
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:36,759
I just feel like I'm dreaming.

63
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:39,020
Fool.

64
00:03:41,959 --> 00:03:43,460
So, are you happy?

65
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:45,900
I'm happy. How about you?

66
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:47,719
I'm okay.

67
00:03:49,419 --> 00:03:51,239
Look at them.

68
00:03:52,932 --> 00:03:56,020
- I'll perform a show for you.
- What show?

69
00:03:56,020 --> 00:03:57,680
Chorus.

70
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,460
Chorus?

71
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:01,279
Kid!

72
00:04:05,999 --> 00:04:09,460
♪ Loving you, walking alone in the dark alley ♪

73
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,819
Childish.

74
00:04:11,819 --> 00:04:16,100
You're so stupid. I can't bear to abandon you. Even kids can bully you.

75
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:18,020
Wait for me.

76
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:23,639
You want to shoot me?

77
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,400
No, no.

78
00:04:29,479 --> 00:04:32,679
- Protect me, protect me.
- Three against one is not fair.

79
00:04:32,679 --> 00:04:34,939
So what if it's not fair?

80
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:04,700
Calm down, calm down. Can't fall into his mire again.

81
00:05:04,700 --> 00:05:06,372
No.

82
00:05:08,359 --> 00:05:10,840
Lu Liuliu, I'm not hungry. I'm not eating.

83
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,619
It's me.

84
00:05:22,919 --> 00:05:25,040
What's up?

85
00:05:28,099 --> 00:05:30,280
Why are you closing the door?

86
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:33,350
Let's talk about the swimming pool.

87
00:05:34,460 --> 00:05:37,739
What's wrong with the swimming pool? How come I don't remember?

88
00:05:37,739 --> 00:05:41,604
♫ The setting sun quietly crossed the sky ♫

89
00:05:41,604 --> 00:05:45,419
♫ Like I've chased you for millions of miles ♫

90
00:05:45,419 --> 00:05:48,355
♫ Could it be the secret of the stars ♫

91
00:05:48,355 --> 00:05:51,199
♫ Rushing to the stars without leaving a trace ♫

92
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,780
Let me help you recall.

93
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:56,694
♫ Fantasizing about us, I can't stop thinking about you ♫

94
00:05:56,694 --> 00:06:00,532
♫ It seems there's a special connection between you and me ♫

95
00:06:00,532 --> 00:06:03,319
♫ I'll take you to the Milky Way and fall into your eyes ♫

96
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:06,400
Jiang Xile, Jiang Xile.

97
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:22,379
Jiang Xile.

98
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:26,019
Jiang Xile.

99
00:06:32,380 --> 00:06:34,279
What's up?

100
00:06:35,499 --> 00:06:39,500
I have something to tell you. Can I come in?

101
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:42,960
Stay away from me. I have nothing to say to you.

102
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:54,099
Jiang Xile, your shoe is outside.

103
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:14,659
This is delicious. You should try it.

104
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:18,620
- Is it delicious?
- Yes.

105
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:23,120
You two, there's so much on the table. Do you have to eat this one together?

106
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:26,028
You can share one with Ding Ran.

107
00:07:26,028 --> 00:07:27,859
Scratch that.

108
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,980
Take your time.

109
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:32,900
It's ready.

110
00:07:32,900 --> 00:07:34,480
Thank you.

111
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,212
It's so delicious.

112
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:43,240
Jiang Xile, you're drinking from Ding Ran's bottle.

113
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,500
I'm sorry.

114
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:48,920
You don't need to dislike me that much.

115
00:07:50,579 --> 00:07:52,879
Here's a new one.

116
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:55,540
I won't drink anymore.
I'm afraid I might drink too much later.

117
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:57,840
You two indirectly kissed.

118
00:07:57,840 --> 00:08:00,980
Lu Liuliu, stop talking nonsense.

119
00:08:05,536 --> 00:08:07,319
What's this?

120
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:10,120
- That's a slice of pumpkin.
- I'll also taste it.

121
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:13,880
Jiang Xile, you have food on your mouth.

122
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:16,299
What is it?

123
00:08:16,299 --> 00:08:17,760
Left side.

124
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,760
Right, right side.

125
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:24,020
Ding Ran, you wipe it for her.

126
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:26,519
- Come on, lean over.
- I have some on my mouth too.

127
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:27,720
Come on, come on.

128
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:31,939
- I'll help you.
- I can do it myself, I can do it myself.

129
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:36,959
Jiang Xile, if you wipe your mouth that way,

130
00:08:36,959 --> 00:08:39,460
you might spark a flame of love.

131
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:41,280
You!

132
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,280
- Don't get so excited.
- Don't get excited.

133
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:46,760
From today on, no one is allowed to mention the mouth to me.

134
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:49,979
What's wrong with the mouth? Why are you so agitated?

135
00:08:49,979 --> 00:08:54,660
Ding Ran. What happened between you today? Was it something related to the mouth?

136
00:08:55,700 --> 00:08:57,779
Nothing happened today.

137
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,979
Nothing?

138
00:08:59,979 --> 00:09:02,279
What about other days?

139
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:04,959
You tell me, I want to hear.

140
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:19,200
There's a bathroom upstairs too. Why do you insist on using the one downstairs?

141
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,340
They're using the one upstairs.

142
00:09:22,079 --> 00:09:24,639
These two people are really…

143
00:09:24,639 --> 00:09:26,500
Jiang Xile,

144
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,579
let's talk later.

145
00:09:33,199 --> 00:09:36,000
You always want to talk to me. What do you want to talk about?

146
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,760
Why can't you say it now?

147
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:41,080
This will make me nervous, confused unconsciously, and overthinking.

148
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,999
I like you.

149
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:56,360
I like you.

150
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,580
I originally wanted to say it more formally.

151
00:09:58,580 --> 00:10:00,800
But today, I…

152
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:03,919
I'm not listening, not listening. All nonsense.

153
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:08,920
Not listening, not listening.

154
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,980
All nonsense.

155
00:10:18,779 --> 00:10:22,199
Impossible, impossible. I must have heard wrong.

156
00:10:29,979 --> 00:10:32,480
Sleep, sleep.

157
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:57,860
No message at all.

158
00:10:57,860 --> 00:11:00,639
He must be messing with me again.

159
00:11:07,059 --> 00:11:09,480
Jiang Xile, I beg you.

160
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:12,879
Go to sleep.

161
00:11:40,939 --> 00:11:43,380
He was really messing with me.

162
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:55,100
I can't do it.

163
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:58,500
Where are you going?

164
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:02,360
I have to get out of here today. If I stay any longer, I'll have problems.

165
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:04,820
What's wrong?

166
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:07,239
Where is Ding Ran?

167
00:12:07,239 --> 00:12:09,260
He went to work.

168
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:12,900
Is this a joke? He just went to work like this.

169
00:12:13,839 --> 00:12:17,580
A good young man, going to work. Is there a problem with that?

170
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:19,460
There's no problem with him.

171
00:12:19,460 --> 00:12:22,400
If I stay any longer, there will definitely be a problem.

172
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,540
Let's go, Liuliu. Pack your belongings and go with me.

173
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:27,630
Me? It takes me two days to pack my belongings.

174
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:29,920
Are you all right?

175
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:32,640
- I'm fine.
- That's good.

176
00:12:33,459 --> 00:12:37,633
[Ding Ran]

177
00:12:37,633 --> 00:12:40,660
[Ding Ran]

178
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:42,400
What do you mean?

179
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,380
Come to the town hospital with Lu Liuliu quickly.

180
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:47,660
Our high school class teacher, Ms. Shen, is hospitalized because of illness.

181
00:12:53,986 --> 00:13:00,600
[2012 Spring] ♫ As darkness falls in the sky, the road appears short, and destiny changes ♫

182
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:05,629
♫ Who can escape judgment by spinning lies? ♫

183
00:13:05,629 --> 00:13:07,420
Ding Ran.

184
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:12,660
What a coincidence, we meet again today.

185
00:13:13,939 --> 00:13:16,380
What are you doing later?

186
00:13:16,380 --> 00:13:20,720
- Going to the library to study.
- Can I go with you?

187
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:25,900
[2012 Summer]
♫ I'm blessed to encounter a meaningful bond ♫

188
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:27,839
Ding Ran,

189
00:13:28,999 --> 00:13:30,780
why are you walking?

190
00:13:30,780 --> 00:13:32,179
My bicycle is broken.

191
00:13:32,179 --> 00:13:34,079
Again? Didn't you get it fixed?

192
00:13:34,079 --> 00:13:36,039
It's not fixed yet.

193
00:13:37,179 --> 00:13:38,779
Get off.

194
00:13:39,734 --> 00:13:43,580
♫ Ten years of missed opportunity, now reunited with regret ♫

195
00:13:43,580 --> 00:13:45,192
Take it.

196
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:49,500
Then how will I go to school?

197
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:53,859
What are you standing there for? I'll give you a ride.

198
00:13:53,859 --> 00:13:55,304
Okay.

199
00:13:55,304 --> 00:13:58,985
♫ Memories of you laughing, crying, and forgotten feelings ♫

200
00:13:58,985 --> 00:14:03,362
♫ The most intimate thoughts turned into nothingness ♫

201
00:14:03,362 --> 00:14:06,157
♫ Missing you is hard to endure ♫

202
00:14:06,157 --> 00:14:12,389
♫ You haunt my dreams, yet you completely ignore me ♫

203
00:14:12,389 --> 00:14:15,356
♫ It dawned on me overnight that after all the twists and turns, I still love you deeply ♫

204
00:14:15,356 --> 00:14:18,972
♫ It dawned on me overnight that after all the twists and turns, I still love you deeply ♫

205
00:14:18,972 --> 00:14:21,944
♫ Back then, I was oblivious, pushing you away and regrets unravel as we reunite ♫

206
00:14:21,944 --> 00:14:26,725
♫ Back then, I was oblivious, pushing you away and regrets unravel as we reunite ♫

207
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:31,039
The school hasn't changed much, but I didn't expect Ms. Shen to have aged a lot.

208
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:33,900
Why did she wait until now to go to the hospital?

209
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:36,939
I heard from Ding Ran that Ms. Shen had been worrying about her students.

210
00:14:36,939 --> 00:14:39,520
So she has been delaying going to the hospital.

211
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:42,220
I've taken the things. Let's go.

212
00:14:42,919 --> 00:14:46,579
Why don't we buy new daily necessities for Ms. Shen?

213
00:14:46,579 --> 00:14:49,519
Why does she have to use these old ones? They have been used to such an extent.

214
00:14:49,519 --> 00:14:51,919
She just doesn't want to waste things.

215
00:14:52,839 --> 00:14:55,079
Ms. Shen doesn't have any children.

216
00:14:55,079 --> 00:14:58,320
She was the nicest to us in high school.

217
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:01,480
Ding Ran, can you help her?

218
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:04,540
Don't worry. I've already spoken to the director.

219
00:15:04,540 --> 00:15:08,439
Tomorrow, Ms. Shen should be able to move to the hospital.

220
00:15:08,439 --> 00:15:12,440
It's good to study. You can help those you want to help.

221
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:16,140
Unlike me. Even if I want to help, I can't do much.

222
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:20,980
You have flexible working hours. You can spend more time taking care of Ms. Shen.

223
00:15:20,980 --> 00:15:23,600
By the way, Liuliu, can you help me give this to Ms. Shen?

224
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,260
Sure.

225
00:15:27,620 --> 00:15:29,600
Where are you two going?

226
00:15:31,299 --> 00:15:33,100
We—

227
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:34,939
Ding Ran.

228
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:49,300
Xu Shanshan.

229
00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:53,140
Ding Ran, long time no see.

230
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:56,820
From the back, I thought it was you. It's really you.

231
00:15:57,500 --> 00:16:00,860
- Long time no see.
- Didn't you say she's had so much cosmetic surgery that her face was stiff?

232
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:04,939
Must have recovered. Appeared after a long time.

233
00:16:04,939 --> 00:16:07,520
Ding Ran, I just came back from Paris.

234
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:10,159
- Paris.
- I heard our high school class teacher, Ms. Chen, is sick.

235
00:16:10,159 --> 00:16:12,719
So I came especially to see her.

236
00:16:14,199 --> 00:16:17,700
She clearly saw in the group that Ding Ran was coming. So she showed up.

237
00:16:17,700 --> 00:16:21,419
Such a lawyer. Our class teacher's surname is Shen, not Chen.

238
00:16:21,419 --> 00:16:23,320
Exactly.

239
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:29,240
Ding Ran, shall we find a place to sit and chat?

240
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:32,259
Xile, the weather has been unpredictable recently.

241
00:16:32,259 --> 00:16:34,659
The weather forecast says it's going to rain later.

242
00:16:34,659 --> 00:16:39,699
Yes, Liuliu, before the sky starts to drop Knives,

243
00:16:39,699 --> 00:16:41,820
let's hurry up and go.

244
00:16:43,139 --> 00:16:46,319
- You go ahead. I'm waiting here for Qi Fei to pick me up.
- All right, bye.

245
00:16:46,319 --> 00:16:48,120
Bye.

246
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:53,179
Sorry, I just got off work. I don't have time to chat.

247
00:16:54,239 --> 00:16:56,099
Ding Ran.

248
00:16:56,099 --> 00:16:59,740
Xu Shanshan, long time no see.

249
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:09,240
What are you looking at?

250
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:11,459
Did you go to True-Beauty Clinic in Building 45

251
00:17:11,459 --> 00:17:15,820
at No. 1199 on Chengqian West Road a month ago?

252
00:17:15,820 --> 00:17:18,079
How... How do you know?

253
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:23,300
Oh, no. Oh no.

254
00:17:23,300 --> 00:17:25,840
Lu Liuliu, is there any problem with that clinic?

255
00:17:25,840 --> 00:17:27,239
Don't leave.

256
00:17:27,239 --> 00:17:29,579
You explain to me, Lu Liuliu.

257
00:17:42,319 --> 00:17:44,080
Why is it raining so hard?

258
00:17:44,080 --> 00:17:46,079
I don't know.

259
00:17:49,099 --> 00:17:50,659
Wait for me, I'll be right back.

260
00:17:50,659 --> 00:17:57,055
♫ I look at you from behind ♫

261
00:17:57,055 --> 00:18:02,779
♫ Behind this street lies a sea of stars ♫

262
00:18:02,779 --> 00:18:09,623
♫ You ignored that sleep talk-like monologue ♫

263
00:18:09,623 --> 00:18:15,540
♫ I rely on you outside of your world ♫

264
00:18:17,114 --> 00:18:23,756
♫ You are the love that's out of reach ♫

265
00:18:23,756 --> 00:18:29,386
♫ But I'm waiting like a child ♫

266
00:18:29,386 --> 00:18:36,281
♫ Endless like sailing, not afraid of being blown away by the wind ♫

267
00:18:36,281 --> 00:18:41,585
♫ The moonlight confesses in my place as I wake up ♫

268
00:18:41,585 --> 00:18:44,789
♫ How did I meet you? ♫

269
00:18:44,789 --> 00:18:49,592
♫ I wait for you to give me your embrace in the mundane world ♫

270
00:18:49,592 --> 00:18:54,440
♫ The past, present, and future have all stopped for you ♫

271
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:56,500
Jiang Xile, let's go!

272
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:59,720
♫ As you walk towards me, dreams are pushed aside ♫

273
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:01,539
Let's go together.

274
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:08,296
♫ Grant me the chance to no longer face the crowd ♫

275
00:19:08,296 --> 00:19:11,528
♫ How did I meet you? ♫

276
00:19:11,528 --> 00:19:16,212
♫ Flipping through the pages of our story ♫

277
00:19:16,212 --> 00:19:22,969
♫ Even if the sea in the palm of my hand is empty, I will not let go ♫

278
00:19:22,969 --> 00:19:29,959
♫ Even if the storm comes again, I don't want to hide ♫

279
00:19:29,959 --> 00:19:38,201
♫ Under your eaves, we meet without feeling like strangers now ♫

280
00:20:11,079 --> 00:20:13,199
Are you all right?

281
00:20:13,199 --> 00:20:14,380
I'm fine.

282
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:17,940
I'm waiting for Liuliu and Qi Fei. She hasn't come back with Qi Fei.

283
00:20:18,820 --> 00:20:20,500
Qi Fei just texted me,

284
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:24,399
saying they have something to do. They might come back late.

285
00:20:24,399 --> 00:20:26,020
Okay.

286
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:33,960
Do you want to have tea?

287
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:36,919
Have tea? No.

288
00:20:38,239 --> 00:20:40,220
Really have tea.

289
00:20:40,959 --> 00:20:42,859
All right then.

290
00:20:49,059 --> 00:20:51,780
Why are you laughing?

291
00:20:51,780 --> 00:20:54,860
When did having tea Have so many meanings?

292
00:20:54,860 --> 00:20:57,239
Isn't that because of Lu Liuliu and Qi Fei?

293
00:20:57,239 --> 00:21:00,120
Didn't they start by "having tea"?

294
00:21:01,159 --> 00:21:04,899
You and Lu Liuliu have been friends for ten years.

295
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,780
Originally, Liuliu and I thought

296
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:12,599
I would be a model and she would be a fashion designer.

297
00:21:12,599 --> 00:21:14,860
We would shine together.

298
00:21:14,860 --> 00:21:16,820
But we didn't expect it to be the other way around.

299
00:21:16,820 --> 00:21:19,920
This world is really… Nothing is certain.

300
00:21:20,660 --> 00:21:22,220
Yes.

301
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:26,260
When I was little, I even thought about being an astronaut.

302
00:21:27,979 --> 00:21:31,919
Why did you become a breast surgeon?

303
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:38,440
When I was a child, I was the type to do everything according to my own plan.

304
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:43,899
There was one thing I did almost all the preparations,

305
00:21:43,899 --> 00:21:46,280
but there was still an accident.

306
00:21:47,239 --> 00:21:52,199
So when the hospital assigned departments, I just wrote that I would obey arrangements.

307
00:21:52,199 --> 00:21:54,719
So I was assigned to the breast surgery department.

308
00:21:55,580 --> 00:21:59,940
Which thing was it? Even with all the preparations, there was still an accident.

309
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:04,699
Confessing to you.

310
00:22:06,059 --> 00:22:13,674
♫ Page by page, the photos look more like full stops  ♫

311
00:22:13,674 --> 00:22:18,839
♫ I'm alone in my room, reminiscing about the past ♫

312
00:22:18,839 --> 00:22:24,639
If it wasn't for Xu Shanshan's doing that day, on the day of the graduation ceremony,

313
00:22:26,959 --> 00:22:29,239
I probably would have confessed to you.

314
00:22:29,239 --> 00:22:38,264
♫ It is a natural part of life for adults to come and go ♫

315
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:44,920
On the way to school every day, what you thought was a coincidence

316
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:49,199
was actually me preparing in advance. I was waiting there.

317
00:22:51,139 --> 00:22:53,980
My bicycle was never broken.

318
00:22:54,919 --> 00:22:56,980
I just wanted to give you a ride.

319
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:06,939
Also, when you called me to wish me a Happy New Year,

320
00:23:09,320 --> 00:23:15,259
I edited a message a long time in advance, wanting to send it to you.

321
00:23:17,284 --> 00:23:20,439
- I…
- Don't think that being in a relationship with me means you can manage my career.

322
00:23:20,439 --> 00:23:22,620
Liuliu, listen to my explanation.

323
00:23:22,620 --> 00:23:24,739
What's wrong, Liuliu?

324
00:23:25,879 --> 00:23:27,516
Liuliu.

325
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:30,220
- Liuliu.
- Don't follow me.

326
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:33,260
It's not what you think, Liuliu.

327
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:40,979
I'll go see what's happening with them.

328
00:23:46,039 --> 00:23:48,060
Is it too late?

329
00:24:14,179 --> 00:24:19,560
I… We should go up and see them first.

330
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:31,940
Liuliu, I…

331
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:35,680
Liuliu, listen to me. I don't mean it that way.

332
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:38,360
Liuliu, I don't mean it that way.

333
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:40,199
If you don't mean it that way, what do you mean?

334
00:24:40,199 --> 00:24:42,800
How dare you pay the rent for my store?

335
00:24:42,800 --> 00:24:46,960
I didn't pay for you. I just waived your rent.

336
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:50,620
All the buildings there belong to our family.

337
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:53,900
No wonder everyone calls you Junior President Qi.

338
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:58,460
I've known you for so long. How did I not know that you are so powerful?

339
00:24:58,460 --> 00:25:01,280
Not really very powerful.

340
00:25:02,979 --> 00:25:06,240
You really can't tell sarcasm from sincerity, can you?

341
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:09,200
You also had someone secretly go to my store to buy my clothes.

342
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:12,460
What, trying to be the overbearing CEO from TV dramas?

343
00:25:12,460 --> 00:25:16,460
Well, if your store isn't doing well, I can't just sit back and do nothing.

344
00:25:16,460 --> 00:25:21,139
Whether my store is doing well or not, it's not up to you to interfere. Do you really have to?

345
00:25:21,139 --> 00:25:25,100
I have to. You can't even afford to pay the rent.

346
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:27,460
Shut up.

347
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:31,279
Liuliu, can you let me finish what I have to say?

348
00:25:35,979 --> 00:25:39,460
I just wanted to help you solve the problem. Nothing else.

349
00:25:39,460 --> 00:25:43,699
Your way of solving problems is to have people go to my shop to buy my clothes?

350
00:25:43,699 --> 00:25:47,659
You're so rich. Why don't you just give me money?

351
00:25:48,999 --> 00:25:52,219
How much do you want? I can transfer it to you now.

352
00:25:55,199 --> 00:25:57,879
What do you think I am?

353
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,139
My girlfriend.

354
00:26:00,139 --> 00:26:02,400
The person I like.

355
00:26:04,739 --> 00:26:06,619
What's wrong?

356
00:26:08,520 --> 00:26:11,000
Nothing. I'll sleep with you tonight.

357
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:12,799
Liuliu.

358
00:26:15,279 --> 00:26:18,100
Nothing. I'll sleep with you tonight.

359
00:26:18,859 --> 00:26:20,939
Who wants to sleep with you?

360
00:26:33,979 --> 00:26:37,719
Liuliu, where's Qi Fei? He hasn't gotten up yet?

361
00:26:39,540 --> 00:26:42,560
I had another argument with him this morning.

362
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:46,279
In a fit of anger, I drove him away.

363
00:26:48,039 --> 00:26:55,179
I thought the four of us could always live in this house.

364
00:26:55,179 --> 00:26:59,500
It wasn't until today that I realized except for me,

365
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:02,259
each of you had your own things to do.

366
00:27:02,259 --> 00:27:05,300
Ding Ran is a doctor, who can heal and save people.

367
00:27:05,300 --> 00:27:10,160
Qi Fei seems to be playing around. But in fact, he can do everything very well.

368
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:14,260
Even though you resigned, you are still drawing new design drafts.

369
00:27:14,260 --> 00:27:18,620
You basically design the clothes we can sell in our store.

370
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:20,300
As for me,

371
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:30,620
I don't even have a home in my hometown.

372
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:37,440
Liuliu, how about I accompany you to see your parents?

373
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:39,020
No need.

374
00:27:39,020 --> 00:27:41,820
They don't lack a daughter like me.

375
00:27:41,820 --> 00:27:44,779
Actually, Qi Fei is quite right.

376
00:27:45,340 --> 00:27:48,240
I have always been unsure about what I want.

377
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:51,140
Nor do I have plans for my future.

378
00:27:52,239 --> 00:27:54,939
I'm just unwilling to admit it.

379
00:27:56,320 --> 00:27:59,200
Enough about me. What about you?

380
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:02,300
Have you made things clear with Ding Ran?

381
00:28:05,039 --> 00:28:08,840
So, what do you think of him now?

382
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:15,380
Liuliu,

383
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:20,359
do you remember what you guys said at that time?

384
00:28:20,359 --> 00:28:25,240
You said even the chicken at the entrance of the village knew that I liked him.

385
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:27,099
Xu Shanshan could also see it.

386
00:28:27,099 --> 00:28:29,980
She was so anxious that she stomped her feet in front of me.

387
00:28:29,980 --> 00:28:32,360
How could he be unaware?

388
00:28:34,059 --> 00:28:39,276
But just because of my one sentence,

389
00:28:39,276 --> 00:28:42,299
he denied all of my feelings.

390
00:28:42,299 --> 00:28:45,660
Now, he suddenly says he likes me.

391
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:49,339
To be honest,

392
00:28:49,339 --> 00:28:53,019
I'm not disbelieving, but angry.

393
00:28:53,019 --> 00:28:55,879
You know. That's Xu Shanshan's problem.

394
00:28:55,879 --> 00:28:58,880
That's not Xu Shanshan's problem, Lu Liuliu.

395
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:01,180
I'm very clear minded.

396
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:04,759
It's just he…

397
00:29:08,839 --> 00:29:11,319
It's just he…

398
00:29:11,319 --> 00:29:13,519
Actually,

399
00:29:14,460 --> 00:29:17,160
he doesn't like me that much.

400
00:29:24,119 --> 00:29:25,839
Xile.

401
00:29:26,420 --> 00:29:28,520
Ding Ran is different from us.

402
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:31,099
He is also different from Qi Fei.

403
00:29:31,099 --> 00:29:33,400
That's just his personality.

404
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:41,300
So I think we all need to calm down.

405
00:29:46,860 --> 00:29:48,539
Liuliu.

406
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:51,600
The vacation is over.

407
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:53,639
Let's go back.

408
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:57,660
Go back? You want to leave Ding Ran here?

409
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,219
Why should I care about him?

410
00:29:59,219 --> 00:30:03,750
Let's go back and start a new life.

411
00:30:13,560 --> 00:30:15,199
Jiang Jiang, let's go.

412
00:30:15,199 --> 00:30:17,740
I'll take you to my fourth aunt-in-law's house to have nice food.

413
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:20,259
Such a good boy, let's go.

414
00:30:20,259 --> 00:30:21,892
Go.

415
00:30:23,919 --> 00:30:25,879
Watch your step.

416
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:35,440
Jiang Xile, I still feel a bit reluctant to leave here.

417
00:30:36,159 --> 00:30:38,099
Even if you're reluctant, you have to be.

418
00:30:38,099 --> 00:30:42,120
If we don't go back to work, we're paying the rent for nothing.

419
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:45,959
- Let's go.
- Go.

420
00:30:47,999 --> 00:30:52,199
Do you think Ding Ran will be shocked If he comes back and finds us gone?

421
00:30:52,199 --> 00:30:56,860
Who cares? When he refused me at that time, he left without a word too.

422
00:30:57,559 --> 00:31:05,161
♫ Page by page, the photos look more like full stops  ♫

423
00:31:05,161 --> 00:31:12,649
♫ I'm alone in my room, reminiscing about the past ♫

424
00:31:12,649 --> 00:31:20,287
♫ No matter how far the lens of memory can reach, it will eventually lose focus ♫

425
00:31:20,287 --> 00:31:29,824
♫ It is a natural part of life for adults to come and go ♫

426
00:31:29,824 --> 00:31:33,296
♫ All these years, we cried and laughed are memories we cherished ♫

427
00:31:33,296 --> 00:31:35,972
♫ All these years, we cried and laughed are memories we cherished ♫

428
00:31:35,972 --> 00:31:41,155
♫ In a blink of an eye, time encourages change ♫

429
00:31:41,155 --> 00:31:45,080
♫ A heart shattered in regrets is hard to mend ♫

430
00:31:45,080 --> 00:31:49,381
♫ It may take several more years to forget those years ♫

431
00:31:49,381 --> 00:31:53,390
♫ My willingness to be cute is not simple ♫
